  "elapsed_s": 310.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They-- some of them took great delight-- some of the German SS troops took great delight in that torture.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] shortly after, a day or so after we had taken the camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this-- General Lyndon started [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] throwing his weight around.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And our commanding general down to my headquarters one morning, it was about a day or two-- two days, I think, after we had taken the cab.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, well, things are heating up here for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, you know, Lyndon is causing a big-- big stink and they're appoint an IG to the 7th Army to make an investigation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, I'm going to send you on home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, our division has been selected to participate in the invasion of Japan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We're going back to the States and we're going to retrain and reequip and then we'll be part of the invasion forces for Japan and you'll be on-- you'll go home and take a-- get a leave and we'll be going back to the States right away and you can rejoin us in the States.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was a little unhappy about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he said, I'll send a command car down for you tomorrow morning and you can-- you can take that command car and take whatever people you want and report to Le Havre, France, which was a port.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was to be assigned to the Assembly Area Command which operated the ports, which is an American Army organization.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call it the Assembly Area Command.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The purpose was to get troops back to the States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the reason for that headquarters.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
